Are there any reasons why the sequences of the episodes are messed up? I mean episodes 121, 120, 117, 118, 122, 119, 123, do not seem to appear in the right order. 

Season 1 Disc 1: episode 721, 103, 104
Season 1 Disc 2: episode 105, 106, 107, 108
Season 1 Disc 3: episode 109, 110, 111, 112
Season 1 Disc 4: episode 113, 114, 115, 116
Season 2 Disc 1: episode 120, 121, 117, 118
Season 2 Disc 2: episode 122, 119, 123, 124
that's because the number represents the recording (NOT THE AIRING) order.  The DVD shows you the episodes as they were aired.  If you'd pay attention to the extras you would know this.
